description:
This is a 19 minute workout called 'Breathwork To Help Support The Release Of DMT (3 Rounds Of Guided Breathing)' from the channel Breathe With Sandy.
The workout falls under Rest/Breathing exercises and Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Deep Recharge and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.
